---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<PageLayout meta={{ title: "Oscar Gilg" }}>
	<section class="space-y-6">
		<h1 class="title">Oscar Gilg</h1>
		<p class="leading-relaxed">
			I work on AI welfare and persona representations at MATS 9.0, mentored by Patrick Butlin
			(Eleos AI). Previously equity options at Optiver, philosophy of consciousness with François
			Kammerer in Bochum, and Maths and CS at Oxford.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-12">
		<h2 class="title text-accent mb-4 text-xl">Research and writing</h2>
		<ul class="list-disc space-y-2 ps-5" role="list">
			<li>
				Personas use a shared preference vector. MATS 9.0 with Patrick Butlin (
				<a
					class="cactus-link"
					href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/pxC2RAeoBrvK8ivMf/models-have-linear-representations-of-what-tasks-they-like-1"
					rel="noreferrer"
					target="_blank">post</a
				>,
				<a
					class="cactus-link"
					href="https://github.com/oscar-gilg/Preferences"
					rel="noreferrer"
					target="_blank">code</a
				>; preprint forthcoming).
			</li>
			<li>
				Split Persona Training. Trigger-conditioned persona fine-tuning. SPAR 2025, under review
				at ICML 2026.
			</li>
			<li>
				<a
					class="cactus-link"
					href="https://github.com/oscar-gilg/zombuul"
					rel="noreferrer"
					target="_blank">Zombuul</a
				>. Claude Code plugin for autonomous research loops on GPU pods.
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-12">
		<h2 class="title text-accent mb-4 text-xl">CV</h2>
		<p>
			<a class="cactus-link" href="/cv.pdf" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank">View CV (PDF)</a>
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-12">
		<h2 class="title text-accent mb-4 text-xl">Contact</h2>
		<ul class="list-disc space-y-1 ps-5" role="list">
			<li>
				Email: <span data-email-user="oscar.gilg18" data-email-domain="gmail.com"
					>JavaScript required, or use the links below</span
				>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a
					class="cactus-link"
					href="https://github.com/oscar-gilg"
					rel="noreferrer"
					target="_blank">github.com/oscar-gilg</a
				>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a
					class="cactus-link"
					href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/oscar-gilg"
					rel="noreferrer"
					target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/oscar-gilg</a
				>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<script is:inline>
		document.querySelectorAll("[data-email-user]").forEach(function (el) {
			var u = el.getAttribute("data-email-user");
			var d = el.getAttribute("data-email-domain");
			var addr = u + "@" + d;
			var a = document.createElement("a");
			a.href = "mai" + "lto:" + addr;
			a.textContent = addr;
			a.className = "cactus-link";
			el.replaceWith(a);
		});
	</script>
</PageLayout>
